# Vendored Reflaxe compiler framework.
#
# This intentionally contains classpath and version metadata only. Reflaxe is
# started exactly once by reflaxe.c.CompilerInit after C-build detection.
# ${SCOPE_DIR} makes this work from every directory inside the checkout.

-cp ${SCOPE_DIR}/vendor/reflaxe/src/
-D reflaxe=4.0.0-beta
